Wajir County Commissioner said the lorry had a total of 93 bales each weighing 5 kilograms.The consignment was intercepted at Hadado within Wajir by police officers manning Lalkuta area. Police in Wajir County are holding two suspected drug traffickers after they were found transporting bhang concealed as cement. 



